dcterms:description: An anonymized research dataset provided by the health provider after risk assessment and data sharing agreement, used for exploratory data analysis and network construction.

dcterms:description: A referral network constructed from consecutive patient consultations, where a connection is established if a patient consults a primary care physician and then a specialist within a month.
